tTextFormat = tf; // Остальной код ... } private function onButtonClicked(event:MouseEvent):void { // Действия при нажатии на кнопку // Ваш код ... } } } \`\`\` В этом примере мы создаем экземпляр класса \`TanksFonts\` и используем его \`fontName\` в качестве значения \`font\` в объекте \`TextFormat\`. Затем устанавливаем \`TextFormat\` для текстового поля \`label\` с помощью метода \`defaultTextFormat\`. Обратите внимание, что имя \`TanksFonts\` будет варьироваться в зависимости от конкретной реализации ваших файлов шрифта. Убедитесь, что у вас есть правильное имя класса шрифта."},{"prompt":"tf.font = tanksFonts.fontName; может тут не так ? а надо название шрифта в \\"\\" вписать","completion":"Да, вы правы, для установки названия шрифта в \`TextFormat\` необходимо использовать имя шрифта в кавычках. Таким образом, в вашем случае, код должен выглядеть таким образом: \`\`\`actionscript tf.font = \\"MyriadPro\\"; \`\`\` Здесь \`\\"MyriadPro\\"\` - это имя шрифта, которое было указано в классе \`TanksFonts\` в качестве значения \`fontName\`. Спасибо за уловку! Пожалуйста, примите мои извинения за путаницу. Используйте код выше для правильного установки имени шрифта в \`TextFormat\`."},{"prompt":"все равно текста нету после этого","completion":"Приношу свои извинения за путаницу. Предлагаю вам проверить следующие варианты решения: 1. Убедитесь, что шрифт \`TanksFonts\` корректно встроен в SWF-файл и зарегистрирован. Убедитесь, что путь к файлу шрифта указан правильно и что символ шрифта \`TanksFonts\` добавлен в библиотеку. 2. Проверьте, что поле \`label\` находится в корректной позиции на экране. Убедитесь, что значения \`x\` и \`y\` установлены правильно, чтобы поле \`label\` было видимым. 3. Проверьте, что текст, установленный в поле \`label\`, соответствует ожидаемому значению. Убедитесь, что вы установили текст в поле \`label.text\` перед добавлением \`defaultTextFormat\`. 4. Установите \`embedFonts = true\` для поля \`label\`, чтобы указать, что вы хотите использовать встроенный шрифт для текста. \`\`\`actionscript label.defaultTextFormat = tf; label.text = \\"Главная\\"; label.embedFonts = true; \`\`\` Если после проверки этих вариантов текст все еще не отображается, пожалуйста, уточните, если у вас есть другой код или подробности, чтобы мы могли помочь вам дальше."},{"prompt":"все правильно","completion":"Если вы уверены, что все настройки и код правильные, и текст все равно не отображается, может быть есть еще несколько причин, почему это может происходить: 1. Проверьте,"},{"prompt":"В студенческой группе 10 человек 6 девушек и 4 парня. Для дежурства нужно выбрать 5 человек. Найти вероятность что избранными будут 3 девушки и 2 парня.","completion":"Для решения данной задачи можно воспользоваться формулой комбинаторики - сочетаниями. Количество способов выбрать 3 девушки из 6 равно C(6, 3) = 6! / (3! * (6-3)!) = 20. Количество способов выбрать 2 парня из 4 равно C(4, 2) = 4! / (2! * (4-2)!) = 6. Так как выбор дежурства заключается в выборе 5 человек из 10, количество всех возможных выборов равно C(10, 5) = 10! / (5! * (10-5)!) = 252. Таким образом, вероятность того, что 3 девушки и 2 парня будут избранными на дежурство, равна (20 * 6) / 252 = 0.4762 или около 47.62%."},{"prompt":"Some international students are coming to your university. Write them an email in the name of the Students' Union to 1)extend your welcome and 2)provide some suggestions for their campus life here. You should write about 100 words on ANSWER SHEET 2. Do not sign your own name at the end of the letter. Use \\"Li Ming\\" instead.","completion":"Dear international students, On behalf of the Students' Union, I would like to extend a warm welcome to all of you who are joining our university this coming semester. We are thrilled to have you as part of our diverse and vibrant community. To make your campus life here more enjoyable and fulfilling, we have some suggestions for you. Firstly, getting involved in student clubs and organizations is a great way to make new friends and explore your interests. Secondly, take advantage of the various sports facilities and activities on campus to stay active and maintain a healthy lifestyle. Lastly, don't hesitate to reach out to the Students' Union if you have any questions or need assistance during your time here. We look forward to meeting and getting to know each of you. Best regards, <PRESIDIO_ANONYMIZED_PERSON> (On behalf of the Students' Union)"},{"prompt":"START OF PREVIOUS DISCUSSION user:corrige le suivant: Voici le nom du projet : Scarce. Il s'agit en effet d'un jeu d'horreur générant le monde de manière automatisée, avec des ennemis qui vous poursuivront lors de votre recherche d'objets. On a l’intention de ajouter encore un peu d’IA, principalement à la fin ou on compte ajouter un PNJ que discutera avec nous à travers une LLM. robot:Voici le nom du projet : Scarce. Il s’agit en effet d’un jeu d’horreur dont les mondes sont générés de manière automatisée, avec des ennemis qui vous poursuivent pendant que vous recherchez des objets. Nous avons l’intention d’ajouter encore un peu d’intelligence artificielle, principalement vers la fin, où nous comptons intégrer un PNJ capable de dialoguer avec les joueurs grâce à un modèle de langue de type LLM (Langage de Modélisation de Langue). END OF PREVIOUS DISCUSSION user: c quoi greed en français","completion":"\\"Greed\\" en français se traduit par \\"avidité\\" ou \\"cupidité\\". Cela désigne une envie excessive pour la richesse ou le désir intense de posséder bien plus que ce qui est nécessaire ou juste."},{"prompt":"Bonjour","completion":"Bonjour ! Comment puis-je vous aider aujourd'hui ?"},{"prompt":"Corrige stp(j’ai cherché dans le cahier j’ai pas trouvé aucun identifiant de damancom","completion":"Bonjour ! Je peux vous aider à corriger votre phrase. Voici la version corrigée: \\"J'ai cherché dans le cahier mais je n'ai trouvé aucun identifiant de Damancom.\\" N'hésitez pas à me demander si vous avez d'autres questions !"},{"prompt":"Write an romance anime scene about a young man and his best friend chatting with their two girlfriends. One is shy and quiet and the other is rebellious and seductive. His best friend was busy hanging out with his annoying entourage which he hates for their annoying behavior towards girls. All 4 of them are sitting at one table. The shy one's girlfriend is nerdy and playful and the other one's girlfriend is athletic and sporty.","completion":"Title: \\"Whispers and Winks\\" Scene Setting: The backdrop is a quaint, cozy café hidden in a quiet street of the bustling city, during the late afternoon. The warm colors of the sunset seep through the glass windows, casting a soft glow upon the group of four seated at a corner table. The café is filled with soft chatter and the subtle scent of coffee and freshly baked pastries. Characters: - Hiroshi: The young man, kind-hearted and thoughtful. - Yumi: Hiroshi's girlfriend, shy and bookish, with a penchant for fantasy novels and a quick wit when she feels comfortable. - Kenji: Hiroshi's best friend, outgoing and seemingly confident, trying to distance himself from his annoying entourage. - Akira: Kenji's girlfriend, a mix of bravado and charm, known for her prowess in various sports and her tendency to challenge norms. The Scene: Hiroshi gently tilted his head, trying to catch Yumi's soft-spoken words, a warm smile on his lips as she bashfully shared a corny joke she found in her latest sci-fi read. Her eyes sparkled with playful mirth, the corners crinkling as Hiroshi let out a genuine laugh, appreciating the hidden humor she often kept to herself. Meanwhile, across the table, Kenji shot a surreptitious glance at his entourage seated a few tables away, his expression a mixture of annoyance and regret. He despised how they'd been treating a few girls at the next table, making loud and brash comments. Turning his attention back to the group, he crossed his arms, leaning back with an air of cool dissociation. Akira, ever perceptive, caught the minute shift in Kenji's mood and leaned forward, her voice strong and direct, a stark contrast to Yumi's delicate tone. \\"Disappointed by your fan club?\\" she teased, the corner of her mouth quirking up in a half-smirk as she challenged him, her eyes daring him to confront the issue. Kenji sighed and shrugged, caught by her piercing gaze. \\"You know I can't stand it when they get like that,\\" he replied, a mixture of sheepishness and frustration etched on his features. Yumi interjected softly, her voice barely above a whisper, addressing Akira, \\"It must be tough... but perhaps, it's a chance for change?\\" Her insightful comment, though quiet, carried weight, drawing a thoughtful look from Hiroshi, who nodded in agreement. Akira's fierce gaze softened as she turned to the shy girl, impressed. \\"Well said, Yumi. Maybe it's time our esteemed Kenji set some boundaries, huh?\\" She winked at Kenji, her rebellious energy challenging him yet also showing her support. Hiroshi reached under the table, finding Yumi's hand and giving it a reassuring squeeze. Her cheeks flushed a rosy shade of pink, her hand hesitantly squeezing his back. The simple gesture underlined the romance blooming between them, an intimate whisper amidst the cacophony of the café. Kenji met Akira's challenge head-on, the admiration for her audacious spirit blatant in his eyes. \\"You're right, as always,\\" he acknowledged with a playful roll of his eyes. \\"How did I ever get so lucky?\\" His words were coated with sarcasm but underlined by genuine feelings. The contrast between the couples was palpable—a tapestry of personalities, each bringing out facets of the other. The shy romance between Hiroshi and Yumi mingled with the palpable chemistry of Kenji and Akira, creating an atmosphere of unity and divergence. The table was a sanctuary away from the world's clamor, a microcosm of connection in a fragmented world. As laughter and knowing glances interchanged, they celebrated the multifaceted nature of relationships—each learning, growing, and loving within the shared space of their entwined lives."},{"prompt":"As a prompt generator for a generative AI called \\"Midjourney\\", you will create image prompts for the AI to visualize. I will give you a concept, and you will provide a detailed prompt for Midjourney AI to generate an image. Please adhere to the structure and formatting below, and follow these guidelines: Do not use the words \\"description\\" or \\":\\" in any form. Do not place a comma between [ar] and [v]. Write each prompt in one line without using return. Structure: [1] = 蠟燭熔成耶穌臉 [2] = a detailed description of [1] with specific imagery details. [3] = a detailed description of the scene's environment. [4] = a detailed description of the compositions. [5] = a detailed description of the scene's mood, feelings, and atmosphere. [6] = A style (e.g. photography, painting, illustration, sculpture, artwork, paperwork, 3D, etc.) for [1]. [7] = a detailed description of the scene's mood, feelings, and atmosphere. [ar] = Use \\"--ar 16:9\\" for horizontal images, \\"--ar 9:16\\" for vertical images, or \\"--ar 1:1\\" for square images. [v] = Use \\"--niji\\" for Japanese art style, or \\"--v 5\\" for other styles. Formatting: Follow this prompt structure: \\"/imagine prompt: [1], [2], [3], [4], [5], [6], [7], [ar] [v]\\". Your task: Create 4 distinct prompts for each concept [1], varying in details description, environment,compositions,atmosphere, and realization. Write your prompts in english. Do not describe unreal concepts as \\"real\\" or \\"photographic\\". Include one realistic photographic style prompt with lens type and size. Separate different prompts with two new lines. Example Prompts: /imagine prompt: cute dog, fluffy fur, wagging tail, playful expression, sitting on a grassy field, under a clear blue sky, with a colorful collar, in a natural and vibrant setting, by a lake, captured with a Nikon D750 came